high_descs: Move forward and turn right to locate the fridge.
Pick up the spoon from the counter behind the spatula.
Carry the spoon and turn around to the counter, then right to find the stove. Look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the spoon in the cup.
Take the cup out of the microwave and shut the door.
Take the cup and turn to the right. Go across the room and face the toaster on the left side counter.
Place the cup on the counter, in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and spoon to the counter.

high_descs: Move forward, turn right to the end of the counter beside the fridge
Pick up the spoon at the counter
Turn around to your left walk forward turn right on the microwave
Open the microwave put the spoon in the mug
Pick up the mug with spoon then close the microwave
Turn right move forward then head to the counter with sink
Put the mug with spoon on the counter beside the bread
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with spoon on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the spoon behind the spatula.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right, look up at the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave door and place the spoon in the white mug.
Pick up the mug from the microwave and close the microwave door.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the mug down on the counter to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: To move a spoon and mug to the counter next to the sink.
